description:
A free, reduced-functionality version of our LabChart data acquisition and analysis software.

LabChart Reader is a free, reduced functionality version of our LabChart data acquisition and analysis software.

With LabChart Reader you can:
- Open LabChart data files
- Import other file formats
- View and scroll through data
- Set up and modify calculations and analysis settings
- Install the Spirometry and Cardiac Axis Extensions
- Analyze data
- Print

LabChart Reader cannot:
- Record new data
- Save data
- Use other analysis modules and extensions
- Send and Publish

For details of the full version of LabChart and our PowerLab data acquisition hardware systems, please see our website at www.adinstruments.com.
Fixes
- Computers with recent Intel graphics drivers will now correctly load past the LC8 splash screen.
